        {
            "+content": "Forty-year-old hitman Juzo Ogami has been living in the shadows his entire life. He tried the wife-and-family thing, but it ended in a divorce, and now he's back to just living for the job. Only his most recent job lands him in some unusual trouble. He accidentally unleashes a genetically-modified wasp, and when it stings him, he's returned to his thirteen-year-old body. The only way to figure out how to reverse things is to get cozy with the daughter of the pharmaceutical group that developed the wasp and take on a dangerous new job: attending middle school.",
